title: Lose Weight WITHOUT Dieting by David Nordmark.epub
description:
Diets don't work. Studies have shown that only 5 percent of people who go on a diet are able to keep the weight off for more than a year. Yet even with this 95 percent failure rate the weight loss industry continues to flood the market with new diets and useless gimmicks. What's the secret to true, long lasting weight loss? The key is to focus on your habits as they are related to food, not dieting.
Genre: Non Fiction, Healthcare, Fitness
